{
  "_doc": [
    "Canonical syscall category definitions for f8.",
    "",
    "TO ADD A SYSCALL: find the appropriate category, add the name to its 'syscalls' array.",
    "TO ADD A CATEGORY: add a new object to the 'categories' array with id, label, color, textColor, description, and syscalls.",
    "Display order follows array order. Colors are from ColorBrewer (https://colorbrewer2.org/).",
    "All tools (f8, f8_analyze, import.js, server.js) read this file — no other source of truth."
  ],

